<h1>Customising authentication credential capture</h2>

<p>The <code>apiExplorer</code> javascript object provides a method to add API keys to an internal list, and a method to inject those
API keys into the explorer page, so that the user can select the key from a dropdown menu instead of having to type it in.</p>

